<div class="row">
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h2 style="margin-left:5px" class="panel-title"><span tal:replace="context/title"/></h2>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:30px; margin-bottom:-10px" class="panel-body">
    <div class="row">


  <div class="col-xs-2 col-sm-1">

    <div style="margin-left:5px" class="btn-group">
      <button class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus">
      </button>
      <ul style="width:200px" class="dropdown-menu">
        <li><a href="#" tal:attributes="href python:context.absolute_url()+'/++add++Kursordner'">Kursordner</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-5 col-sm-6"><h4>Meine Kurse</h4></div>
  <div class="col-xs-5 col-sm-5"></div>


  </div>
</div>
<hr>
</div>

<div tal:condition="view/inhalte" class="row">

  <div tal:condition="view/kursordner" class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12">
      <h3 style="margin-top:1px">
        <img style="width:32px;height:32px;margin-left:20px;" tal:attributes="src string:${view/statics}/images/folder.png"> 
          <span style="margin-left:10px">Kursordner</span>
      </h3>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row" tal:repeat="ordner view/kursordner">
    <div class="col-xs-2 col-sm-1">
      <a tal:attributes="href string:${ordner/url}/delete_confirmation" title="Ordner löschen">
        <span style="font-size:130%;color:red;margin-left:24px" class="glyphicon glyphicon-minus-sign"/>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-10 col-sm-11">
      <h4 style="margin-top:1px">
        <a tal:attributes="href ordner/url"><span tal:replace="ordner/description"/> (<span tal:replace="ordner/title"/>)</a>
      </h4>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<div tal:condition="not:view/inhalte" class="row">
 <div class="col-xs-2 col-sm-1"></div>
 <div class="col-xs-9 col-sm-9">
   <h4>Dein persönlicher Bereich ist noch leer!</h4>
   <p>Mit Klick auf <img style="width:16px;height:16px;margin-left:3px;margin-right:3px" title="add-2.png" 
      tal:attributes="src string:${view/statics}/images/add-2.png"> kannst Du neue Kursordner hinzufügen.</p>

   <div style="margin-top:16px;" class="row">
     <div class="col-xs-1 col-sm-1">
       <img style="width:32px;height:32px;" class="img-responsive" tal:attributes="src string:${view/statics}/images/folder.png">
     </div>
     <div class="col-xs-9 col-sm-9">
       <p>In den <strong>Kursordnern</strong> speicherst Du die Übungsaufgaben für Deine Schüler und Studenten. Lege hier für
          jeden Deiner iTunes U Kurse einen Kursordner an.</p>
     </div>
     <div class="col-xs-2 col-sm-2"></div>
   </div>

 </div>
 <div class="col-xs-1 col-sm-2"></div>
</div>
